                        <condition key="deficient">The front board is re-used, and attached to the
                           text block in reversed position. The leather cover of the front board and
                           of the spine is partly missing; of the back board partly detached. The endbands are missing. The manuscript was resewn; the sewing is damaged. 
                           Some 10 initial quires of the text block are loose and crudely attached with recent threads.
                           <ref target="#q1"/> is loosely attached to the text block, <ref target="#q9"/> and <ref target="#q17"/> are partly detached from the text block.</condition>
